faceoff_positive.comments: I purchased these for the smaller things in my pantry-nuts, seeds etc. and they do seem air tight, as long as you snap down the lid until it clicks. The lids aren't as tight as I would prefer, but they are great if you have arthritis-not the struggle others are to open. They are easy to hand wash but not dishwasher safe. If you have something powdery or fine, it can get caught in the groves on the underside of the lid, so don't fill right to the brim. My only real complaint is the The Home Edit gals did not design them to fit inside their multi purpose bin, which I also use. Seems short sighted & surprising from these detail oriented gals! I have tried every combination of sizes but there will always be a gap. I accepted that & use them anyway, but turned a couple on their sides at the front of the bin.
faceoff_positive.headline: Great Multi Use Canisters

faceoff_negative.comments: We have to store our stuff in a locker before we leave work. I needed a box to put my laptop and accessories into. I measured my laptop and looked at the measurements of the box and it seems to be the right side. Lo and behold, I get the box and my laptop doesn't fit. They should put the dimensions of the interior of the box in the description and not the exterior.
faceoff_negative.headline: Sizing was wrong

details.comments: When you put everything in the turntable, it is so heavy that the turntable is not functional.  I even tested with 3 - 5 sauces and it was doing the same.  I don't understand how this happens.  I dont even think its a defective product, I bought 3 and all of them were the same.  Very disappointing.
details.headline: DOES NOT TURN, really it does not turn

details.comments: I was using plastic products and slowly replacing them with this.  They hold up well, are easy to clean and keep my products fresh.  I recommend them highly!

details.comments: Bought this yesterday and will return immediately because it does not turn properly.  I tried it and it was jerky and did not turn smoothly and then got stuck. One would think that for this money they could have designed something that turned smoothly.  Very poor quality.
details.headline: Does not turn
details.merchant_response: We are sorry to hear this product did not meet your expectations. We strive to provide quality products at a competitive price. Please contact our Customer Solutions Department so we can make it right. They can be reached at 1-888-CONTAIN (266-8246).

details.comments: I tried this product for two weeks. Put spinach in the greensaver, hoping it would help with moisture control, but the lid doesn't click on and it didn't keep the spinach edible for longer than the packaging the spinach comes in. The size was good for my fridge drawers, but that's about it.
details.headline: Doesn't work

details.comments: These Linus Pantry Bins are perfect for my pantry organization!  I bought a few to check them out and then placed an order for more!  Great quality product, easy to see what's in them.  I use them for my daughter's snacks and also seasoning packets.  You could use them for so many things in so many areas!  Highly recommend!!
details.headline: Perfect for pantry storage
details.merchant_response: Thank you for sharing about your experience with this product! Many customers will benefit from it.

details.comments: The bin is just the right size & shape for the items I put in it, plus super quality
details.headline: Just what I needed

details.comments: I use these to organize refrigerated items.  Now I can find what I want in a glance.  Great product.
details.headline: I have bought more of this product

details.comments: The dimensions listed in the product description are for the top part of the basket, which is wider than the storage bin itself. I can still make these work for what I intended to use them for, but it is disappointing to have less interior space after spending a good amount of time reading through product descriptions to find the size I needed. Also, the lids fit loosely on the top of the basket, which gives the entire set-up an overall cheap feeling. At least the components are made out of recycled plastic.
details.headline: Dimensions are incorrect
details.merchant_response: The dimensions we provide are of the outermost exterior of our products. Images 6, 7, and 8 show both exterior and interior dimensions. We appreciate your feedback and will pass it along to our product buyers as we aim to meet the needs of every customer.
